00:21:03,488 --> 00:21:04,888
Tidak.

327
00:21:04,888 --> 00:21:08,388
Tapi aku sangat sibuk sehingga sering kali hanya akan masuk kotak suara.

328
00:21:10,188 --> 00:21:12,588
